parameters:
"And so, I ended up having to clean up his mess... Huh? Does
it smell weird in here?"

"Huh?... Now that you mention it, it does stink. Hey,
Master. Is something burning in the kitchen?"

"Huh? The stove in this place is broken, you know? What's
there to burn?"

"Hey, hey! Isn't that the alarm going off? There really is
something burning in the kitchen!"
"That's ridiculous! How could anything be... Oh, crap."

"Geez!? The sprinklers went off! Damn it! My clothes are all
wet now!"

"There goes my good drink! What are you gonna do about this,
huh?"

"Shut up!! I have no idea what's going on either! Everyone
get out, now! You too, missy, move it!"
